# Output Directory

This directory contains the generated output files from the A-Level question perturbation pipeline.

## Generated Files

When you run `python script.py`, the following files will be created here:

1. **`1_transcribed.jsonl`** - Transcribed questions from input images (JSONL format)
2. **`2_perturbed.jsonl`** - Perturbed versions of the transcribed questions (JSONL format)
3. **`3_validated.jsonl`** - Questions that passed validation (JSONL format)
4. **`4_final_document.tex`** - Final compilable LaTeX document with all validated questions
